---
title: Double Plant-Based Chick'n Tenders & Mash with Caramelised Onion Sauce & Steamed Veggies
description: We better set an extra place at the table tonight because nostalgia is coming over and it’s bringing this veggie version of homey chicken and potato mash. Cook up a caramelised onion sauce to put a spin on this classic.
